articles.author: Jordan Garcia
articles.title: Intuitive Machines 2 Lunar Landing - NASA (.gov)
articles.description: Carrying NASA technology and science, Intuitive Machines is targeting no earlier than 12:32 p.m. EST on Thursday, March 6, to land its lunar lander on the Moon.
